void SET_MULTIPLAYER_BANK_CASH();Preview image:To change the bank balance use STAT_SET_INT with "BANK_BALANCE" to whatever value you need to.Examples:C#// Code to show both Money and Bank HUD
N_0x170f541e1cadd1de(true);
SetMultiplayerWalletCash();
SetMultiplayerBankCash();
N_0x170f541e1cadd1de(false);

// Add a delay to let the player read his money
await Delay(5000);

// Hide both Bank and Money HUD
RemoveMultiplayerWalletCash();
RemoveMultiplayerBankCash();

